  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 175°C.",
    "In a bowl, mix flour and sugar until well combined.",
    "Add baking powder and Worcestershire sauce; stir gently but thoroughly.",
    "Fold in vegetable oil and eggs using a spatula.",
    "Stir in chopped nuts for added texture and crunch.",
    "Pour batter into a mason jar lined with plastic wrap or parchment paper to prevent sticking.",
